org.apache.streams.dropwizard

Class GenericWebhookResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.streams.dropwizard.GenericWebhookResource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, StreamsOperation, StreamsProvider

    public class GenericWebhookResource
extends Object
implements StreamsProvider
    GenericWebhookResource provides basic webhook connectivity.

    Add processors / persistWriters that read from "GenericWebhookResource" to consume data posted to streams.
